```
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY         (Production, Preview, Development)
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY    (Production)
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET     (Production, Preview, Development)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL       (Production, Preview, Development)
OPENAI_API_KEY           (Production)
```

### **n8n** (RackNerd VPS):
- Stored in n8n credentials manager
- Access via n8n API with Bearer token

