## 📊 DATA STORAGE HIERARCHY

### **Priority Order** (ALWAYS follow this):
1. **PRIMARY**: n8n Data Tables (workflow data, leads, logs)
2. **SECONDARY**: Airtable (dashboards, manual config, reporting)
3. **TERTIARY**: Notion (documentation only, 15-20 strategic docs)

### **Never Store In**:
- ❌ MongoDB (unless customer project >50K records)
- ❌ Supabase (unless custom customer app with real-time requirements)

