## 🎯 QUICK DECISION TREE

### "Where should this code go?"
- Public website content? → **Webflow** (rensto.com)
- API endpoint? → **Vercel api.rensto.com** (`/apps/web/rensto-site/src/app/api/`)
- Admin dashboard? → **Vercel admin.rensto.com** (`/apps/web/admin-dashboard/`)
- Customer portal? → **Vercel portal.rensto.com** (`/live-systems/customer-portal/`)
- Workflow automation? → **n8n** (173.254.201.134:5678)

### "Which database should I use?"
- Workflow data? → **n8n Data Tables**
- Dashboards/config? → **Airtable** (sync from n8n every 15 min)
- Documentation? → **Notion** (high-level only)
- >50K records? → **MongoDB** (customer projects only)
- Real-time app? → **Supabase** (customer projects only)

